1. *Fali* nam još jedan komad. (We are missing one more piece.)
2. Ono što *fali* ovom slikaru je još jedan detalj. (What this painter is missing is one more detail.)
3. Ona ne zna šta joj *fali* da bi završila ovaj zadatak. (She doesn't know what she is missing to finish this assignment.)
4. *Fali* mi još jedan dokaz da bih potvrdio moje tvrdnje. (I'm missing one more proof to confirm my claim.)
5. Ne znam šta bih još mogao da uradim, čini se da mi *fali* inspiracija. (I don't know what else I could do, it seems like I'm missing inspiration.)